<figureCitation box="[1055,1125,1877,1897]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="14.[147,174,1459,1476]" captionTargetBox="[147,1442,151,1423]" captionTargetId="figure-273@14.[146,1442,147,1423]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Fig. 13. Neighbor-joining distance tree of 27 COI sequences of Vanewrightia gen.nov. and 38 of its neighbors from BOLDSYSTEMS (2019) with BIN BOLD codes. Distances (normalized to 1) are given below each branch (omitted if &lt;0.002) and bootstrap supports above each branch (in bold, only if&gt;70%) obtained with MEGA7 (Kumar et al. 2016). For Vanewrightia, the collection sites are highlighted by colors. Scale bar = 1%." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5384279" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5384279/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
